imdb.plot outline: Mayo Clinic, one of the world's most trusted medical centers, and Gaiam are happy to introduce an integrated health action plan. While there is no known cure for diabetes, there are ways to manage -- and maybe prevent -- the condition. In this video you'll discover how body weight affects diabetes and discover lifestyle changes that might make your condition just a little easier to live with. Changing the way you live can change the way you feel.
